### Crear pago: usa Transit para cifrar PAN y credenciales dinámicas PostgreSQL para persistir
POST http://localhost:8080/payments/v1/payments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "merchantId": "mrc-001",
  "amount": 120.50,
  "currency": "USD",
  "cardPan": "4111111111111111"
}

